{"tid":1960262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國動物園一隻老虎對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陽性","createTime":"2020-04-06T04:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T09:03:12.000Z","uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1da3681c284b630adac1b9b8260436d13938bfc6","tid":1960262,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"美國紐約市布朗克斯動物園一隻老虎，被驗出對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陽性反應，相信是全球首宗老虎感染個案。<br />\n<br />\n動物園表示，染病的是一隻4歲的馬來亞虎，牠的姐姐、另外兩隻東北虎及三隻非洲獅亦出現乾咳症狀，部分表現出氣喘和食慾不振。動物園相信，牠們是被園內一名無出現病徵的職員傳染，強調所有動物目前情況良好，有望康復。<br />\n<br />\n動物園上月16日已經因應疫情，暫時關閉。美國獸醫協會和聯邦疾控中心重申，出於謹慎起見，建議新型肺炎患者應該限制與動物接觸。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519065-20200406.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519065-20200406.htm&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=299bef91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519065-20200406.htm&h=4efd312f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519065-20200406.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b2f2b1e6b7ae73c653ea59b623ab2a6ae8b2fc0e","tid":1960262,"uid":17359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>武漢肺炎</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"47878906c321b0e1c2d0e4316a0357e8c51f78fd","tid":1960262,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b2f2b1e6b7ae73c653ea59b623ab2a6ae8b2fc0e","tid":1960262,"uid":17359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>武漢肺炎</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"823746920a3108528ccebb2cb8e5a61930bb589e","tid":1960262,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:55:37.000Z","msg":